name: Whitsunday Crocodile Safari
description: Experience the thrill of seeing estuarine crocodiles in their natural habitat in the Whitsundays. This unique Australian nature tour offers an up-close look at the diverse wildlife and vegetation of the region's estuaries and wetlands. Enjoy a calm water adventure cruise on the Proserpine River, where you can observe 'Salties' and other fascinating wildlife.
includes: Undercover tables, seating, toilet facilities, drinking water, refreshments
highlights:
Estuarine crocodiles in natural habitat
Wildlife and vegetation of Whitsunday coastline
Calm water adventure cruise
Proserpine River mangrove ecosystem
Local historical significance of campsite
